        "body": "<p>I don't think there's any comment to check the day of the week in the spring.<\/p>\n<p>You may need to use the following methods:<\/p>\n<pre><code>public void checkDate() {\n    \n    LocalDate localDate = LocalDate.now();\n    \n    DayOfWeek dayOfWeek = localDate.getDayOfWeek();\n    \n    if(dayOfWeek == DayOfWeek.SATURDAY || dayOfWeek == DayOfWeek.SUNDAY) {\n        // ...do something\n    }\n    \n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
